> Is the gasket that is between the throttle and air dist. box still available
> anywhere?

Porsche dealer 022 133 073A.
 
> How do you disconnect the linkage between the throttle and EGR valve? It looks
> like both ends are held on with a circular keeper that was pressed on and will
> probly be dammaged when I try to remove it.

Undo the linkage by rotating the hexbar in the middle.
 
> I am also thinking about taking the EGR valve apart for cleaning. Do I just
